introduction: Overview (3)Date of Birth	12 August 1992, Wildomar, California, USABirth Name	Jordan Alexa ArentzHeight	 5' 8" (1.73 m)Mini Bio (1)Jordan Arentz is an American model, actress, and writer living in southern California. She was raised by her parents who are both artists of Italian and Scottish descent. Aside from modeling and acting, she is a makeup artist and a contributing writer and editor to several websites focusing on raising awareness to the stigma of mental illness.
